NOW LIVE ✨ The What To Flex fashion show. It’s all about bringing new energy to old pieces for the new season. We’re celebrating by releasing a new category on @depop called “What To Flex" — a collaboration for the side hustlers who flex their 
own style.

👀 how #GalaxyS21 Ultra 5G, #GalaxyZFold2 5G and #GalaxyZFlip 5G make the perfect accessories for these refreshed looks featuring @angelmoret @breerunway @emilycanham @_chasingthreads_ @myabenway @loserthrift @nmillz and @odellmun.

Click the link in our bio to learn how Samsung Galaxy helps your hustle.
